\begin{aligned}
& \mathrm{T}_{\mathrm{r}+1}={ }^{11} \mathrm{C}_r\left(2 x^2\right){ }^{11-r}\left(\frac{1}{2 x}\right)^r \\\\
& ={ }^{11} \mathrm{C}_r 2^{11-r} x^{22-2 r} 2^{-r} x^{-r} \\\\
& ={ }^{11} \mathrm{C}_r 2^{11-r} x^{22-3 r}
\end{aligned}
$$
<br/><br/>Now, $22-2 r=10$ and $22-3 r=7$
<br/><br/>$$
